latestPosts.caption:
✅ Tip 1: Hydrate your skin daily – inside & out
💧 Drink enough water + moisturise daily = effortless glow
✅ Tip 2: Don’t try new skincare a week before
🚫 No new serums, facials or actives – protect your skin from last-minute breakouts
✅ Tip 3: Ice your face for 2 minutes before makeup
🧊 It tightens pores, depuffs, and gives a smooth base naturally
✅ Tip 4: Prep your lips every night
💋 Dry lips = cracked lipstick. Use lip balm + light scrub at bedtime
✅ Tip 5: Match your makeup to your personality – not trends
🌸 Soft glam, bold glam — choose what makes YOU feel beautiful and confident
